WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
Mould Remediation requires specialised knowledge and meticulous documentation.

00:08.000 --> 00:16.000
The S520 standard governs professional mould remediation practices.

00:16.000 --> 00:24.000
Key elements include: containment protocols, negative air pressure, HEPA filtration, and post-remediation verification.

00:24.000 --> 00:32.000
RestoreAssist provides S520-compliant report templates, tracks remediation progress, and maintains complete audit trails.

00:32.000 --> 00:40.000
Documentation is essential for insurance claims and health department compliance.